    <section>
        <title>Introduction</title>
        <para><classname>Majisti\Application</classname> is the main entry point
            or facade into using the entire library. Concrete implementations
            are bootstrapped using an instance created by the
                <classname>Manager</classname>. This is where configuration are
            merged, resources loaded and a Zend_Application bootstrapped.</para>
